{"about_the_game":"Loss is a <strong>3D, First-Person, Exploration, Puzzle, Action, Adventure &amp; Horror</strong> game. You'll play as a teenage boy, who wakes up one night only to find out that all of his family is gone. Where did they go? Why is he alone? Who are these strange ghosts roaming around the house? While solving this mystery, you will explore your house, grab items and keys, unlock doors, solve puzzles, find hidden notes and much more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/GifNew2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1737583414\" /><br><br>The creatures you'll find are rather aggressive too, so you'll have to fight back! With the help of your flashlight, you can point it at the enemies for a few seconds to kill them. This exciting combat will always keep you on the edge, and it is a nice change of pace from the slower puzzle-solving sections.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/LossGIF2-ezgif.com-speed.gif?t=1737583414\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737583414","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/page.bg.jpg?t=1737583414","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737583414","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737583414","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3145980,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Loss is a <strong>3D, First-Person, Exploration, Puzzle, Action, Adventure &amp; Horror</strong> game. You'll play as a teenage boy, who wakes up one night only to find out that all of his family is gone. Where did they go? Why i